            <thetext>This bug only affects non-IE browsers (Firefox, Safari, etc.)

This fix this issue one can set the &quot;overflow-x&quot; to &quot;visible&quot; -&gt; &quot;__getWrappedContent&quot;.

Pro: when inserting large images scrollbars are automatically shown.
Con: when inserting large portions of text WITHOUT a blank scrollbars will also be shown (very uncommon usescase, though).</thetext>
